{"word":"προαγωγός","slug":"προαγωγός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προαγωγός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:προάγω'><el>προάγω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>one who leads on: a pander, pimp, procurer</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a negotiator</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}